<div class="bg-[#858585] h-14 sticky top-0"></div>
<div class="flex">
    <div
        class="text-[{{ fontSize }}px] space-y-[{{ spaceBetween }}px] p-2 box-border overflow-y-auto bg-[#D9D9D9] h-lvh w-[360px] flex flex-col font-['Segoe UI Historic'] font-bold">
        {{#each menus}}
        {{> menu this}}
        {{/each}}
    </div>
    <div id="targetPage" class="flex flex-col mt-10 ml-10 text-justify">
        <p>Your goal is to find the menu: <span class="font-bold">"{{ promptName }}"</span></p>
        <p>Once you find it, click on it and a Done button will appear below. Good luck!</p>
        <div class="self-center">
            <button id="doneBtn" class="border rounded-lg py-3 px-5 bg-green-500 hidden">Done</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>